INSERT INTO `cr_car_reviews` VALUES (1,'Excellent value for money. Excellent safety features gave us confidence Never had a single mechanical issue Perfect companion for our business travel Will book with them again for sure.',4,16,52,NULL,'published','2024-04-06 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(2,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the comfort level was quite good but the car showed some wear and tear. Reasonable option if you\'re not picky Fair value for money.',3,9,6,NULL,'published','2025-10-17 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(3,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Performed flawlessly under all conditions A truly exceptional experience from start to finish This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,27,41,NULL,'published','2024-10-29 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(4,'Great rental experience! Great sound system The car was running smoothly and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. The radio presets weren\'t cleared but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,30,6,NULL,'published','2024-06-29 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(5,'Great rental experience! Excellent fuel economy The car was clean and well-maintained and handled beautifully on both city and highway. The pickup process took a while but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,32,67,NULL,'published','2025-09-25 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(6,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was in excellent mechanical condition and handled beautifully on both city and highway. Minor scuff on the bumper but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,28,87,NULL,'published','2025-08-30 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(7,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Excellent customer service Great choice for anyone needing a reliable car Just a small issue with a small scuff on the rear bumper but nothing major.',4,18,94,NULL,'published','2025-01-02 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(8,'Standard rental car. The car was clean and functional The pickup process took a while Reasonable option for basic transportation Met basic expectations.',3,14,47,NULL,'published','2024-11-16 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(9,'Great rental experience! Spacious interior The car was running smoothly and was surprisingly quiet and smooth. The radio presets weren\'t cleared but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,27,15,NULL,'published','2026-02-22 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(10,'Perfect car for our conference! Premium seating that rivals luxury vehicles The performance was absolutely flawless Service that sets the gold standard Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,14,15,NULL,'published','2024-09-26 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(11,'Very pleased with this rental. Well-maintained and cared for vehicle Made the rental process seamless Perfect for business or leisure travel Just a small issue with the owner\'s manual being missing but nothing major.',4,23,61,NULL,'published','2024-04-30 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(12,'Terrible experience with this car. The engine was making strange noises The vehicle was in poor condition and was making concerning noises. Would not recommend to anyone. Customer service was unhelpful when I reported the issues.',1,12,50,NULL,'published','2025-10-17 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(13,'Outstanding rental experience! Whisper-quiet cabin and smooth ride The car was immaculate in every detail and provided effortless acceleration. The team was absolutely wonderful to work with Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,4,39,NULL,'published','2025-12-24 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(14,'Perfect car for our wedding! Premium seating that rivals luxury vehicles Incredible power delivery and smooth operation The customer service was world-class Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,18,11,NULL,'published','2025-04-09 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(15,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Reliability that exceeded all expectations Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,9,20,NULL,'published','2025-10-12 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(16,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly The car felt stable and well-balanced Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is the pickup location was hard to find. Highly recommend!',4,19,7,NULL,'published','2025-03-01 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(17,'Very pleased with this rental. High-quality materials and finishes Made the rental process seamless Excellent option for families Just a small issue with one cup holder being a bit loose but nothing major.',4,19,25,NULL,'published','2024-05-30 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(18,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was very reliable and was surprisingly quiet and smooth. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,8,11,NULL,'published','2024-11-24 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(19,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Excellent customer service Great choice for anyone needing a reliable car Just a small issue with the pickup location being slightly hard to find but nothing major.',4,11,44,NULL,'published','2024-07-12 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(20,'Average rental experience. Average car for an average price The GPS was a bit outdated but the staff was professional. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,29,57,NULL,'published','2024-05-21 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(21,'Standard rental car. No major issues during our rental The radio presets weren\'t cleared Meets expectations without exceeding them Met basic expectations.',3,5,56,NULL,'published','2024-11-02 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(22,'Average rental experience. Nothing particularly stood out about this rental Could use a bit more trunk space but the car was clean. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,14,3,NULL,'published','2024-03-31 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(23,'Perfect car for our conference! Every passenger commented on the amazing comfort The performance was absolutely flawless Exceptional attention to customer needs Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,27,98,NULL,'published','2024-07-28 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(24,'Decent car for the price. The air conditioning was effective one cup holder being a bit loose but overall acceptable for business trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,14,91,NULL,'published','2025-08-29 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(25,'Great rental experience! The car was clean and well-maintained The car was clean and well-maintained and was surprisingly quiet and smooth. The radio presets weren\'t cleared but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,30,69,NULL,'published','2025-07-02 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(26,'Great rental experience! Spacious interior The car was very reliable and had plenty of power when needed. The radio presets weren\'t cleared but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,9,54,NULL,'published','2024-05-13 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(27,'Terrible experience with this car. There were scratches and dents all over The vehicle was showing significant wear and was making concerning noises. Would not recommend to anyone. Customer service was unhelpful when I reported the issues.',1,12,63,NULL,'published','2025-02-13 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(28,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Quality that rivals the finest vehicles Service that sets the gold standard Incredible bang for your buck Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,15,44,NULL,'published','2026-02-07 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(29,'Absolutely fantastic! Advanced capabilities that impressed everyone Performed flawlessly under all conditions Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,1,78,NULL,'published','2025-01-07 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(30,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Very helpful with directions Will be my go-to rental company Just a small issue with the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but nothing major.',4,15,43,NULL,'published','2025-01-13 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(31,'Great rental experience! Very comfortable seats The car was spotless inside and out and handled beautifully on both city and highway. The radio presets weren\'t cleared but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,28,51,NULL,'published','2024-07-13 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(32,'Great rental experience! Great sound system The car was very reliable and had plenty of power when needed. Minor scuff on the bumper but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,20,73,NULL,'published','2025-09-13 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(33,'Standard rental car. No major issues during our rental Could use a bit more trunk space Nothing exceptional but nothing terrible Met basic expectations.',3,18,47,NULL,'published','2024-07-12 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(34,'Perfect car for our family road trip! Unparalleled comfort for long-distance driving The performance was absolutely flawless The customer service was world-class Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,21,30,NULL,'published','2025-02-05 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(35,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Quality that rivals the finest vehicles Staff went above and beyond at every step Worth every penny and more Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,8,84,NULL,'published','2025-01-28 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(36,'Absolutely fantastic! State-of-the-art amenities throughout Performed flawlessly under all conditions Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,15,5,NULL,'published','2025-12-06 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(37,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable The engine performed well on both city and highway Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is the car manual was missing. Highly recommend!',4,4,20,NULL,'published','2024-04-14 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(38,'Disappointing rental experience. The communication with staff was problematic and The interior was dirty and smelled bad. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,28,10,NULL,'published','2025-10-11 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(39,'Standard rental car. Reliable for basic driving The radio presets weren\'t cleared A typical rental car experience Met basic expectations.',3,21,74,NULL,'published','2024-08-06 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(40,'Below expectations. Could use a bit more trunk space The car was adequate for the price point but The pickup/return process. The pickup process was smooth but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,11,72,NULL,'published','2025-09-23 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(41,'Absolutely fantastic! State-of-the-art amenities throughout Not a single issue throughout our entire rental Absolutely outstanding in every possible way This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,32,5,NULL,'published','2024-07-20 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(42,'Decent car for the price. The sound system worked fine the pickup location being slightly hard to find but overall acceptable for weekend getaway. Would consider again if needed.',3,25,90,NULL,'published','2026-01-21 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(43,'Horrible condition vehicle. Multiple warning lights were illuminated I felt unsafe driving it. The parking brake was sticking Customer service was rude when I complained.',1,30,99,NULL,'published','2024-12-14 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(44,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable Good handling in various driving conditions Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,28,85,NULL,'published','2026-02-09 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(45,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was mechanically perfect and exceeded all performance expectations. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,10,14,NULL,'published','2025-03-20 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(46,'Decent car for the price. The air conditioning was effective the owner\'s manual being missing but overall acceptable for family road trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,23,53,NULL,'published','2025-07-24 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(47,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine Exceptional attention to customer needs Outstanding value for the price paid Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,25,42,NULL,'published','2025-11-25 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(48,'Decent car for the price. The handling was predictable a small scuff on the rear bumper but overall acceptable for weekend getaway. Would consider again if needed.',3,9,26,NULL,'published','2024-06-11 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(49,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Plenty of legroom for everyone Good handling in various driving conditions Impressed all our passengers Only minor complaint is the return process was slightly confusing. Highly recommend!',4,7,2,NULL,'published','2026-01-15 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(50,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was very reliable and was surprisingly quiet and smooth. The GPS was a bit outdated but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,3,90,NULL,'published','2025-08-01 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(51,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Luxury-level quality throughout The customer service was world-class Outstanding value for the price paid Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,24,24,NULL,'published','2026-01-04 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(52,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly The car felt stable and well-balanced Impressed all our passengers Only minor complaint is the car manual was missing. Highly recommend!',4,6,72,NULL,'published','2024-07-11 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(53,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly Started every time without hesitation Perfect companion for our business travel Will book with them again for sure.',4,31,14,NULL,'published','2025-03-17 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(54,'Absolutely fantastic! State-of-the-art amenities throughout Performed flawlessly under all conditions A truly exceptional experience from start to finish This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,32,8,NULL,'published','2025-10-21 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(55,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the technology features were helpful but the pickup process was slower than expected. Gets you from point A to point B Fair value for money.',3,28,80,NULL,'published','2026-02-11 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(56,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was in excellent mechanical condition and was very fuel efficient. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,9,92,NULL,'published','2024-05-05 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(57,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Very helpful with directions Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but nothing major.',4,19,7,NULL,'published','2025-08-31 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(58,'Decent car for the price. The air conditioning was effective a small scuff on the rear bumper but overall acceptable for weekend getaway. Would consider again if needed.',3,15,93,NULL,'published','2025-09-30 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(59,'Perfect car for our business trip! Unparalleled comfort for long-distance driving Performance that rivals much more expensive cars Staff went above and beyond at every step Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,20,77,NULL,'published','2024-10-02 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20'),(60,'Decent car for the price. The sound system worked fine the pickup location being slightly hard to find but overall acceptable for vacation. Would consider again if needed.',3,20,39,NULL,'published','2025-08-23 08:26:20','2026-03-06 08:26:20');
