content-columns quantity=\"2\" content_1=\"Our team of certified professionals ensures that every service is delivered with the highest standards of quality and care. We use only genuine parts and industry-approved methods to maintain your vehicle. Customer satisfaction is our top priority. We understand that your time is valuable, which is why we offer flexible scheduling and quick turnaround times for all our services.\" content_2=\"We offer competitive pricing without compromising on quality. Our transparent pricing policy means no hidden fees or unexpected charges. Our team of certified professionals ensures that every service is delivered with the highest standards of quality and care. We use only genuine parts and industry-approved methods to maintain your vehicle.\"][/content-columns]\n\n[content-images quantity=\"2\" image_1=\"news/8.jpg\" image_2=\"news/6.jpg\"][/content-images]\n\n<h6>Conclusion</h6>\n\n<p>Choosing the right rental car involves more than just picking a vehicle that looks good. By considering the purpose of your trip, the number of passengers, the terrain, fuel efficiency, and your budget, you can select a car that will make your journey smooth, comfortable, and enjoyable. Take your time to compare options and book in advance to ensure you get the best vehicle for your needs. Whether you\'re hitting the open road or navigating city streets, the right rental car can make all the difference in your travel experience.</p>\n',215,NULL,'once','news/2.jpg','icons/mer.png','published','2026-03-06 08:25:15','2026-03-06 08:25:15'),(3,'Car Wash & Detailing Package','Enhance your car rental or repair experience with our premium car wash and detailing service, leaving your car spotless inside and out.','<h6>Determine Your Trip Purpose</h6>\n\n<p class=\"neutral-1000\">The first step in choosing the right rental car is to clearly define the purpose of your trip. Are you traveling alone or with family? Is it a business trip or a leisure vacation? The pur